00:00:28.257 --> 00:00:31.677 line:90% position:50% align:center
to the Saturday afternoon portion
of the program,

00:00:31.677 --> 00:00:34.764 line:90% position:50% align:center
we will learn what we individually can do

00:00:34.764 --> 00:00:37.683 line:90% position:50% align:center
