can disrupt our peace

00:12:56.219 --> 00:12:58.513 line:90% position:50% align:center
and that of others.

00:12:58.513 --> 00:13:00.515 line:90% position:50% align:center
During the next symposium,

00:13:00.515 --> 00:13:03.602 line:90% position:50% align:center
we will consider things we must avoid

00:13:03.602 --> 00:13:07.773 line:90% position:50% align:center
